            <note xml:id="foot.f2">See letters to G. W. Child, [6 May 1868] and 6 May [1868] and n. 3.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">Nomination to the professorship of botany at Oxford, for which Child was a candidate, was vested in the <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_4101.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Royal College of Physicians</ref> (<ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_3684.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Historical register of the University of Oxford</hi></ref>, p. 60).</note>
